---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import TopBar from '../components/TopBar.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Kontakt - Skontaktuj się z nami | Medykalni"
  description="Masz pytania o szkolenia, projekty lub rekrutację? Skontaktuj się z Medykalni - odpowiemy na wszystkie pytania."
>
  <TopBar />
  <Header />

  <main>
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-background-lighter to-white py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Skontaktuj się z nami
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Odpowiemy na wszystkie pytania o szkolenia, projekty i rekrutację
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Dane kontaktowe + formularz -->
    <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
          <!-- Lewa strona - informacje -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">
              Dane kontaktowe
            </h2>

            <!-- Telefon -->
            <div class="mb-8">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                    Telefon
                  </h3>
                  <a href="tel:+48881489851" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark transition-colors text-lg font-semibold">
                    +48 881 489 851
                  </a>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1">
                    Pon-Pt: 9:00 - 17:00
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Email -->
            <div class="mb-8">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                    Email
                  </h3>
                  <a href="mailto:kontakt@medykalni.pl" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark transition-colors text-lg font-semibold">
                    kontakt@medykalni.pl
                  </a>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1">
                    Odpowiadamy w ciągu 24h
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Social media -->
            <div class="mb-8">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
                Śledź nas w mediach społecznościowych
              </h3>
              <div class="flex gap-3">
                <a href="#" class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors text-primary">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"/>
                  </svg>
                </a>
                <a href="#" class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-accent hover:text-white transition-colors text-accent">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zm0-2.163c-3.259 0-3.667.014-4.947.072-4.358.2-6.78 2.618-6.98 6.98-.059 1.281-.073 1.689-.073 4.948 0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98 1.281.058 1.689.072 4.948.072 3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98-1.281-.059-1.69-.073-4.949-.073zm0 5.838c-3.403 0-6.162 2.759-6.162 6.162s2.759 6.163 6.162 6.163 6.162-2.759 6.162-6.163c0-3.403-2.759-6.162-6.162-6.162zm0 10.162c-2.209 0-4-1.79-4-4 0-2.209 1.791-4 4-4s4 1.791 4 4c0 2.21-1.791 4-4 4zm6.406-11.845c-.796 0-1.441.645-1.441 1.44s.645 1.44 1.441 1.44c.795 0 1.439-.645 1.439-1.44s-.644-1.44-1.439-1.44z"/>
                  </svg>
                </a>
                <a href="#" class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors text-primary">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
                  </svg>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Dodatkowe info -->
            <div class="bg-background-lighter rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">
                Biuro
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">
                Medykalni
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                ul. Przykładowa 123<br>
                00-000 Warszawa
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Prawa strona - szybki kontakt -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">
              Wyślij wiadomość
            </h2>
            <div class="bg-background-lighter rounded-2xl p-8">
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                Masz pytania o szkolenia, projekty lub rekrutację? Zadzwoń lub napisz – odpowiemy na wszystkie pytania.
              </p>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <a
                  href="tel:+48881489851"
                  class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 bg-primary text-white px-6 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-dark transition-colors font-semibold text-lg w-full"
                >
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
                  </svg>
                  Zadzwoń teraz
                </a>

                <a
                  href="mailto:kontakt@medykalni.pl"
                  class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 bg-accent text-white px-6 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-accent-light transition-colors font-semibold text-lg w-full"
                >
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                  </svg>
                  Napisz email
                </a>
              </div>

              <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-gray-300">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
                  W czym możemy pomóc?
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                    Informacje o szkoleniach i zapisach
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                    Dołączenie do projektów rozwojowych
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                    Rekrutacja specjalistów dla placówek
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                    Współpraca i partnerstwa
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ kontaktowe -->
    <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-background-lighter">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">
          Najczęściej zadawane pytania
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <details class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 group">
            <summary class="font-bold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
              <span>Jak szybko otrzymam odpowiedź?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
              </svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">
              Na emaile odpowiadamy w ciągu 24 godzin w dni robocze. Telefony odbieramy od poniedziałku do piątku w godzinach 9:00-17:00.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 group">
            <summary class="font-bold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
              <span>Czy mogę umówić się na rozmowę telefoniczną?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
              </svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">
              Tak, wystarczy wysłać email z propozycją terminu, a my skontaktujemy się z Tobą w uzgodnionym czasie.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 group">
            <summary class="font-bold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
              <span>Czy mogę odwiedzić Wasze biuro?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
              </svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">
              Pracujemy głównie zdalnie, ale spotkania osobiste są możliwe po wcześniejszym uzgodnieniu terminu. Skontaktuj się z nami, aby umówić spotkanie.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
